column1: Weekly Initial Claims by Colorado County

column3: Source: Colorado Department of Labor and Employment

The county-level claims data are NOT directly comparable to the state-level data the Department submits to the Employment and Training Administration every week.  Totals differ due to timing and definitional differences between this collection of claims data and the official weekly figures.  Please use the Colorado Total (column C) if you want to want to compare a county to the state.
